Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
parameters a=29'-6" parameters b=59' lock "a", "b"
!if rout_size<6'-6" then parameters rout_size=6'-6"
values{2} "iVolleyNetType" NETTYPE_MEN, `Для Мужчин`, NETTYPE_WOMEN, `Для Женщин`
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values{2} "iDet2D" DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE, `Простой` values "gs_resol" range [3, )
if gs_cont_pen<=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=4 if line_cont_pen<=0 then parameters line_cont_pen=4
if gs_fill_pen<=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91 if line_fill_pen<=0 then parameters line_fill_pen=91 if runout_fill_pen<=0 then parameters runout_fill_pen=91
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then lock "gs_resol"
if rout_area_x<0 then parameters rout_area_x=0 if rout_area_y<0 then parameters rout_area_y=0
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iDet2D DETLEVEL_2D_SIMPLE = 1 DETLEVEL_2D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iVolleyNetType NETTYPE_MEN = 1 NETTYPE_WOMEN = 2
Symbol.Comment: Поле для волейбола с дополнительной областью для выхода.
